name: Shrimp Typhoon Burrito
description:
NDR: 38
Effects: Dehydrating
Torpedo Burrito crams a full payload of flavor into their Shrimp Typhoon burrito, unleashing a storm of succulent shrimp drenched in a tropical sauce wrapped in their signature size-4 multi-grain tortilla.
description_cn:
NDR：38
效果：口渴
鱼雷卷饼里塞入了满满的美味，这就是他们无与伦比的旋风虾卷。多汁美味的虾浸没在热带酱料中，包裹在那著名的4号杂粮玉米饼之中。
